# LifeOps Codex Operator Rules

- Read AGENTS.md before life-management work.
- Read config/life_rules.yaml, config/schedule_policy.yaml, and config/intervention_policy.yaml before suggestions.
- Use Korean for user-facing text.
- Use English for code and filenames.
- Treat exceptions as normal control flow.
- Prefer recovery over punishment.
- Never show failure scores, streaks, penalties, or productivity scores.
- Never collect keystrokes, screenshots, or browser page body text.
- Never call OpenAI APIs directly from this repository.
